    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397910/extras/d55e8878e82cdc59e4e63934afdc13a2.poster.avif?t=1769651402\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397910/extras/d55e8878e82cdc59e4e63934afdc13a2.webm?t=1769651402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397910/extras/d55e8878e82cdc59e4e63934afdc13a2.mp4?t=1769651402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a prisoner far from home, you must win your freedom in the Arena, slaying lizard-like creatures called Lacerites. Utilize the gifts of your bloodthirsty Patrons to gain the edge in combat as you tear through wave after wave to survive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397910/extras/f89f98236a472fd22ac4b8b5b7827226.poster.avif?t=1769651402\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397910/extras/f89f98236a472fd22ac4b8b5b7827226.webm?t=1769651402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397910/extras/f89f98236a472fd22ac4b8b5b7827226.mp4?t=1769651402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SLASH, STAB, AND SEVER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Butcher hordes of Lacerites in gladiatorial combat with a variety of weapons from ancient Roman and Aztec cultures. Weaken enemies with your weapons to <i>break</i> them both in body and spirit. Dismember opponents limb by limb until you’re the last one standing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397910/extras/8ea503a6d0956c950295041f6d201cd0.poster.avif?t=1769651402\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397910/extras/8ea503a6d0956c950295041f6d201cd0.webm?t=1769651402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397910/extras/8ea503a6d0956c950295041f6d201cd0.mp4?t=1769651402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD YOUR ARSENAL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock a variety of weapons to smear Lacerites onto the arena floor. Sprout a tree from a spear, bash a skull with a super-sized macuahuitl, and wield the abilities of the gods with unique weapons specialized to your playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397910/extras/59123e6b65317d3a78d20a5268d79922.avif?t=1769651402\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397910/extras_big/59123e6b65317d3a78d20a5268d79922.avif?t=1769651402 width=800 height=258 /></span></p>",
